        <item>
            <title>【評測】M4 MacBook Air 天藍色新款，實機相片多角度觀賞 + Apple 賣大包效能大提升</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/m4-macbook-air-2/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=m4-macbook-air-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/m4-macbook-air-2/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 13:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Air]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1296963</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 正式推出 M4 MacBook Air，在同一個機殼之下，繼 Apple M2、M3 處理器之後推出到第 3 個升級－－全新 MacBook Air 搭載 M4 處理器。相信好多朋友都喜歡當年 M2 MacBook Air 新機殼四四方方，誠實厚重設計，而且所有配色都比較淺色，清淡但夠高貴顯雅。今年 Apple 更加推出新色「天藍色」，我們以下會給大家多看新機的相片，當然也會詳細介紹與評測。</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00708-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00708-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00708.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>天藍色新色真機圖片共賞<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>手指紋黏附情況已有改善</h2><p>今次得到 Apple 協助我們借來了最新「天藍色」M4 MacBook Air 新機。同大家在 Apple 官網看到的圖片相比，我們看到實物更加高貴大方，最主要是它的顏色並不「過於搶眼」，在充足的光線下更似有點染藍的銀色。而在室內燈光下，你會看到銀色底上面滲出粉藍色。同之前的星光色一樣，藍色色調不會過於搶眼。</p><p>M4 MacBook Air 同樣使用抗指紋表面塗層。過去 M2 MacBook Air 時其午夜暗色被用家指容易吸手指紋，即使在天氣乾燥的環境之下，都是好易吸手指模。而在今次淺色機身上，不容易黏上手手指紋，即使黏上也較容易使用布質材料抹去。但當然它並非完全抗指紋，如果你的手指充滿油脂的話，還是先抹乾手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00706-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00706-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00706.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296969" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00712-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00712-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00712.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00716-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00716-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00716.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00722-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00722-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00722.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>大家看到現時 Apple 只提供 M4 版 MacBook Air，去除了過往保留舊版的選項。而升級 M4 處理器後售價依然維持 HK$7,999 起。新機最大特點是 CPU 處理器由 8 核心升到 10 核心，在基本配置下統一記憶體有 16GB、記憶體頻寬由上代 100GB/s 增至 120GB/s。用家可付費添置多至 32GB 記憶體，比上代多了 8GB。對於需要進行影片剪輯，但又不至於買 MacBook Pro 的朋友，便有更彈性的選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296973" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05214-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05214-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05214-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲我們發現在不同燈光環境之下，天藍色 MacBook Air 又會變成較偏向銀的色調</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00739-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00739-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00739.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在太陽光底下，又有另一個獨特樣貌</p><p>Apple 並未有將最先進 Thunderbolt 5 下放到 Air 系列，但對絕大部份 Air 用户來説，兩個 Thunderbolt 4 的 USB-C 插頭已經十分夠用，因為它已經兼容 USB4 標準。而香港一般電腦用家，在市面買到的硬碟、SSD、快閃手指其實大多數都是 Thunderbolt 3/USB4/USB 3.2 Gen 2，基本上不是問題。</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-1-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-1-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><h2>效能提升 25.6% 非常顯著</h2><p>今代 M4 處理器最大特色是增加了 2 個 CPU 核心，處理器搭配 10 核心 CPU、10 核心 GPU，用電增強但 Apple 也在電池上面輕輕加大了容量，由 52.6 瓦時加大到 53.8 瓦時。應用上我們不覺它比 M3 版的 MacBook Air 更耗電，新舊型號電池耗用基本上持平。</p><p>實際在跑分方面，今代 M4 處理器在 Geekbench 6 的基本單核分數為 3719 分，比對上代提升達 23.6%，可説是一個非常大的升幅；多核分數更加有 14846 分，比對上代提升 25.6％。今代 M4 MacBook Air 可説是非常有誠意。</p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"></td><td valign="top">M4 MacBook Air</td><td valign="top">M3 MacBook Air</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">單核心測試</td><td valign="top">3719 (+23.6%)</td><td valign="top">3009</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">多核心測試</td><td valign="top">14846 (+25.6%)</td><td valign="top">11817</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/m4-macbook-air-2/notebook/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Sony 測試 AI 驅動遊戲角色，已將《Horizon》 Aloy AI 化</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 12:55:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1296815</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>SONY 正研發人工智能驅動的 PlayStation 遊戲角色，先導項目以《Horizon Forbidden West》的主角 Aloy 為原型。該技術由 SONY 先進技術小組與 Guerrilla Games 合作開發，已於內部展示。首個演示於 2024 年前完成，並於 11 月東京技術交流展覽展出進階版本。</p><p>SONY 先進技術小組開發的 AI 版 Aloy 可透過語音指令與玩家對話，採用 OpenAI 的 Whisper 進行語音轉文字，結合 GPT-4 及 Llama 3 處理對話與決策。語音生成則用上 SONY 自家的 Emotional Voice Synthesis（EVS），面部動畫由內部 Mockingbird 技術支援。雖然演示在 PC 上運行，但 SONY 已測試於 PS5 上執行部分功能。</p><p>網上資料顯示，SONY 早在 2025 年 2 月提交專利，探索 AI 助手為玩家提供遊戲指引，顯示其對 AI 技術的長期投入。此此 AI 原型展示 SONY 在遊戲互動技術上的突破。若成功整合至 PS5 或未來平台，可提升玩家體驗。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/news/626695/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 750 元有找進軍平價市場，沈寂多時終於有新機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/htc-wild-fire-e5-plus/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=htc-wild-fire-e5-plus</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/htc-wild-fire-e5-plus/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 12:25:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[htc]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1296844</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>台灣知名手機品牌 HTC 在沉寂多時後，近日於海外市場推出新機 HTC Wildfire E5 Plus。這款入門級智能手機於 2025 年 3 月在越南及泰國等東南亞地區上市，主打大螢幕、長續航及高像素相機，價格親民，在越南售價僅 2,379,000 VND（約港幣 735 元），鎖定基礎使用需求的消費者。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 配備 6.745 吋 HD+ 螢幕，支援 90Hz 更新率，提供流暢的視覺體驗，適合日常瀏覽社交媒體或觀看影片。電池容量達 5000mAh，能滿足一天甚至兩天的使用需求，對於不常充電的用家而言頗具吸引力。據《Gizmo China》報道，該機在越南售價僅 2,379,000 VND（約港幣 735 元），性價比突出，定位清晰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>相機方面，HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 搭載 50MP 主鏡頭及 2MP 景深鏡頭，足以應付日常拍攝，前置則為 16MP 鏡頭，滿足自拍及視像通話需要。處理器採用 Unisoc T606，搭配 6GB RAM 及 128GB ROM，支援 microSD 卡擴充，基本運行流暢，但不適合大型遊戲。系統預載 Android 14，並保留 3.5mm 耳機孔及 USB Type-C 接口，功能實用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296888" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 的推出顯示品牌有意在東南亞市場尋求突破，憑藉低價策略或能吸引新興市場消費者，未來能否擴展至其他地區仍視乎市場反饋及品牌策略調整。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481456790_1090648873-694x273.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="273" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481456790_1090648873-694x273.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481456790_1090648873-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2025/03/09/htc-wildfire-e5-plus-launched-with-6-74-inch-display-50mp-main-camera/">Gizmo China</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61573908089181">HTC Thailand</a>、<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/htc_wildfire_e_plus-11948.php">gsmarena</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
