        <item>
            <title>「北斗短信」行山節實際應用，為香港行山者帶來通訊新保障</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/beidoupackage/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=beidoupackage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/beidoupackage/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技潮人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 11:25:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[戀上山]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[運動科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[北斗短信]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[北斗衞星]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293255</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港人熱愛行山，但山區信號覆蓋有限，通訊中斷的情況時有發生。中國移動香港在 2025 年行山節上推出的「北斗短信」服務，為行山者提供在無地面網絡覆蓋環境下的通訊保障，確保行山人士無論身處何處，都可與外界保持聯繫。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294390" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294407" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲中移動香港行山節之中，亦有應用「北斗短信」技術</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294408" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲北斗體驗台讓公眾親身測試發送短信</p><h2 class="p3">無信號環境下求助與報平安</h2><p class="p3">「北斗短信」依託中國自主研發的北斗衞星系統，即使在手機無信號的情況下，滿足緊急通訊要求，透過特定終端發送帶有定位資訊的文字短信。北斗短信允許用户最多發送 20 個漢字（可發送位置，佔用 2 個漢字）、最多接收 6 個漢字。行山者在迷路、受傷或遇上突發情況時，能迅速發出求救信息，並提供確切位置，協助救援單位及時應對。行山者亦可利用此服務向家人報平安，減少親友擔憂。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1294399 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1-694x357.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="357" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1-694x357.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「北斗短信」運作示意圖</p><div>如何發送北斗短信：用户進入北斗衞星短信界面，編輯內容後根據提示進行搜星發送，至多可發送 20 個漢字（可發送位置，佔用 2 個漢字），最多同時向 4 個用户發送。接收北斗短信的用户將收到短信內容。</div><div></div><div></div><div>如何回復北斗短信：客户在接收到北斗短信後可在 3 天內編輯短信進行回覆，最長 6 個漢字。北斗短信用户進入北斗衞星短信界面，點擊接收按鈕，根據尋星界面指引接收回覆短信。</div><div></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1-694x370.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1-694x370.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1.jpg 983w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">簡單易用<b></b>無需更換手機號碼</h2><p class="p3">與傳統衞星通訊設備不同，「北斗短信」的使用方式更為簡便。行山者無需額外購買昂貴的專業設備，只需透過普通手機，啟用北斗短信服務，即可在無信號時發送文字及位置資訊。這種「不換卡、不換號」的設計，大大降低了使用門檻，適合所有行山愛好者。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
